com.interpss.core.aclf.adj

Interface PSXfrPControl

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BranchFlowControl, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IAclfAdjustment, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PSXfrPControlImpl

    public interface PSXfrPControl
extends BranchFlowControl
    A representation of the model object 'PS Xfr PControl'. PSXfrPControl class. Control power flow at from or to side by adjusting the PSXfr angle. Object id is the same as the branchId it reference to.

    The following features are supported:

    • Acc Factor
    See Also:
    AclfAdjustPackage.getPSXfrPControl()
